## 2. Launching and Running the Web Server

To run this API backend, make sure you have `fastapi` and `uvicorn` installed, then launch it from your machine terminal:

```bash
pip install fastapi uvicorn pydantic
uvicorn emegir_api:app --reload --port 8080

```

Once running, your local engine infrastructure goes live at `http://127.0.0.1:8080`. FastAPI will also automatically generate complete interactive swagger documentation for you at `http://127.0.0.1:8080/docs`.

